data.description: This 2020 build, 3,619sq.ft. home is the perfect abode for your family. Step inside, and you’re greeted by the open foyer with an in-home office to the right and a grand staircase featured to the left. On the first level, you have an open floor plan with an eat in kitchen which is open to the living room. It features modern appliances including a gas stove, and ample counter and pantry space. The master suite has tons of natural light and is complete with an attached bathroom and ample closet space. The second floor features a media room and 3 bedrooms that offer the ideal space for family or invited guests. Enjoy the lovely Texas weather in your private backyard with covered patio. Millwall Drive is situated in a newly established neighborhood in Mckinney, known for its strong sense of community. It's the perfect place for families and individuals alike. Conveniently located to a Community Center, shopping, dining, and adjacent to top rated Reeves Elementary.
